## Lesson template

```markdown
### Lesson N — Short title (YYYY-MM-DD, Wave/feature)

**Context:** what was happening (snapshot of wave/feature in 1-2 lines)

**Root cause:** why it happened (5 whys to something actionable)

**Mitigation:** what changed
- AGENTS.md: <before> -> <after>
- Issue template: <before> -> <after>
- auto-merge gate: <before> -> <after>
- Other: ...

**Trail:** PR #<N>, Paperclip Issue ID `<id>`, run log ID `<id>`, commit `<hash>`

**Tag:** [issue-template | agents-md | gate | quota | tooling | infra | branching]
```

